    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "关羽",
        "张辽",
        "曹操"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四马童同上，甘夫人、糜夫人坐车同上。曹操随曹仁、李典、徐晃、夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、曹"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "洪、张辽出城迎接同上。甘夫人、糜夫人同入城。关羽上，旗牌捧银盘跪迎，献上，关羽下马，曹操迎入城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹仁、李典、徐晃、夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、曹洪、张辽同随下。曹操、关羽、四马童、曹仁、李典、徐晃、"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、曹洪、张辽同上，关羽、曹操同坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知吾二位皇嫂，居住何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫已命人安排馆舍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待某去问皇嫂金安。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌捧金盘跪献，马童接，关羽上马，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张辽听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你去至馆舍，将关羽与甘、糜二夫人，安置在一处，以乱他君臣之礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
