        "程昱",
        "马童"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂、曹仁、李典、徐晃、夏侯惇、乐进、许褚、曹洪、张辽、程昱、曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "关羽为人真可敬，\n话不虚传果是真。\n准备酒宴贺群英。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这般时候为何还不见关羽到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "将身来在宝帐等、程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想必来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关将军到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童引关羽同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨日老夫奉送将军红袍一件，今日为何不见穿来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽掀袍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这不是丞相所赠之袍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军为何这等的俭朴，一件红袍能值几何，为何还用旧袍遮盖？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相有所不知，这新袍乃是丞相所赠，旧袍乃是吾兄长所赐，旧袍穿在外面，\n见袍如见兄长，不敢得新而忘旧也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。\n来，看宴伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军今日为何来迟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某身驱魁重，所乘之马，十分瘦小，况又多病，故而来迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾营中倒有一骑好马，只是生性太劣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某家所用马童，颇能服劣马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就请将军唤他前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马童走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可能骑劣马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人能骑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾营中后糟之上，有一红马，你与吾速速牵来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知丞相之马，有何贵重之处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此马遍体皆赤，日行千里，夜行八百，只是其性过劣，竟无人敢乘骑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童牵马上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此马果然不差，只是可惜无有鞍鞯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有鞍鞯。\n马童，速将鞍镮鞦鞯取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此马老夫曾经乘骑一次，被它摔将下来，险伤性命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鞍鞯到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速速备来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马童备马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待某乘骑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军须要小心，这马劣得很哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马童，带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上马，走圆场，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看关羽身体魁梧，威风凛凛，上得马去，人高马大，犹如天神一般，真虎将也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上，转场，下马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此马生来世间稀，身如火炭果出奇。左右两腋生麟甲，逐电追风快如飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好马呀，好马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军可知此马之来历耶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非虎牢关前，吕布所骑之赤兔马乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然也！将军真好眼力。将军口称好马，莫非有爱马之意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好马人人皆爱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，将此马就送与将军如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相此话当真？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待某大礼相谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽行大礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军自到许昌，老夫相待以礼。上马献金，下马献银，三日一小宴，五日一大\n宴，又赠美女、锦袍，并未见将军道一谢字。今日赠马一匹，竟这样大礼相谢，\n岂非轻人而重畜么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想吾关羽，终日思念兄长，今见此马，日行千里，仰蒙丞相恩赐，若得兄长的\n下落，一日即可相见矣，故而拜谢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀！曹操呀，曹操！你这一计又错了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "躬身施礼把话言，\n细听关某说根源："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "良骥千里名不虚传。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "桃园恩义深似海，\n他思念刘备常挂怀。\n倒叫老夫枉费心裁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
